Mozelle Britton https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mozelle_Britton 0 Mozelle Britton (May 12, 1912 – May 18, 1953) was an American movie actress and columnist. Born in Oklahoma City, Oklahoma, she relocated to southern California when she was seventeen years old. Mozelle_Britton ( May_12_,_1912 – May_18_,_1953 ) was an_American_movie_actress_and_columnist .
